    "synopsis": "Brakus Andradus was once a sniper in the Astra Militarum; now he is a deserter trying to drink away what he saw on his last expedition into the Blackstone Fortress. When a deadly plague erupts and begins to kill the inhabitants of the frontier station Precipice, Brakus is forced back into the vast alien fortress to hunt for a cure. His only companions are a wary Eldar ranger, Amallyn, and a lethal dark eldar gladiatrix, Maugra — uneasy allies whose own goals could turn on him at any moment. A tense standalone novella of survival and old wounds set in the depths of the Blackstone Fortress.",
